","msg":"不過，日本方面的馬迷，已為即將迎來「雷神」雀躍萬分，昨日凌晨時分，在社交媒體twitter已有逾18,000條關於雷神的推文，當中大部份是熱烈期待「雷神」登陸日本馬圈的回應。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n誰會珍惜 當你還擁有"},{"pid":"15d2f5b6182cffd6a77d2379ddcda8d011e9911a","tid":695222,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d71319cc7a834b312cbd17cb92124459be0831de","tid":695222,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T05:40:08.000Z","msg":"成段嘅精粹係 為了子女 就轉戰日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"連外國人都驚咗香港教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a50d4a0714cbb748a6f2ca483c7f00796cbbe9e","tid":695222,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T06:16:18.000Z","msg":"陳加甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}